  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the ordered pair x comma y\"></span> is a solution to the system of equations above, which of the following is a possible value of <span class=\"italic\">x</span>?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
